77
00:04:22,815 --> 00:04:27,820
as they adventure, they get better at what they do and they increase their various stats,

78
00:04:27,820 --> 00:04:32,685
which might make them great at magic or swordsmanship or inspirational singing or something.

79
00:04:32,685 --> 00:04:38,971
The narrative itself is a collaboration between players and one very special player called

80
00:04:38,971 --> 00:04:42,074
the game master, though not in a totally equitable style.

81
00:04:43,095 --> 00:04:46,336
