85
00:04:53,859 --> 00:04:54,780
who needs their help,

86
00:04:54,780 --> 00:04:56,841
how difficult the challenges they face are,

87
00:04:56,841 --> 00:04:58,942
the GM introduces all of these during play

88
00:04:58,942 --> 00:05:00,622
by describing what the characters see,

89
