00:06:30,072 --> 00:06:32,574
according to all of the tinder that we've brought

124
00:06:32,574 --> 00:06:34,515
and lit together as people at the table.

125
00:06:35,680 --> 00:06:39,543
So counter-intuitively, even though they're called role-playing games,

126
00:06:39,543 --> 00:06:43,866
embodying a character, totally not necessary as a defining component.

127
00:06:43,866 --> 00:06:46,509
Many folks prefer the term story games.

